\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"a victory\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 999}, {\"ngram\": \"the only men\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1060}, {\"ngram\": \"three consecutive gold medals\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1097}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsin individual events\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Disappointment, of course, but do not underestimate how the British great has seized victory from the most improbable position following a turbulent period in his life after the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1328, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Disappointment\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the most improbable position\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1261}, {\"ngram\": \"a turbulent period\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not sad at all,\\\" Peaty maintained.\", \"from\": 1330, \"to\": 1370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you are willing to put yourself on the line, there is no such thing as a loss.\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1418}, {\"ngram\": \"no such thing\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"a loss\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am happy with a silver.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1481, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a silver\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's sport, I got blindsided, but it wasn't meant to be.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1492}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This journey, 14 months, it's not