 powerful combination would reignite the fire from within and ensure he climbed back up.\", \"from\": 3801, \"to\": 3917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3809}, {\"ngram\": \"a powerful combination\", \"from\": 3828, \"to\": 3850}, {\"ngram\": \"the fire\", \"from\": 3866, \"to\": 3874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peaty was angered at the mere sight of Qin collecting the medals he viewed as his own and many tipping the 25-year-old to succeed him in Paris without a fight.\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 4077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3957, \"end\": 3960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"score\": 0.9822534298182133, \"rank\": 0.017529711596241417, \"text\": \"Qin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qin_Shi_Huang\"}, {\"begin\": 4055, \"end\": 4060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.931747537693348e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 3918, \"to\": 3923}, {\"ngram\": \"the mere sight\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 3953}, {\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3982}, {\"ngram\": \"a fight\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4076}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That assumption rankled with Peaty, who once again leaned heavily on coach Mel Marshall, seen more as a \\\"second Mum\\\", to deliver the tough love he needed.\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4232, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That assumption\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4093}, {\"ngram\": \"Peaty\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4112}, {\"ngram\": \"coach Mel Marshall\", \"from\": 4147, \"to\": 4165}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"second Mum\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4193}, {\"ngram\": \"the tough love\", \"from\": 4207, \"